data.description: Very spacious 4 BR/2BA/2 car garage & has a heated Pool with screened lanai.  There are even 2 extra rooms that could be used for a den/office/dining/or gaming room.  The house sits with the peaceful Roslyn Canal behind them and across the street from Alhambra Lake in SW Cape Coral.  You might even say a peninsula.  There are plenty of water activities to do right from your own back yard dock with boatlift on the canal with access to 9 Freshwater lakes.  The home has tile, new carpet, brand new roof (2022) that comes with a 30 yr GAF Warranty that includes labor & product.  Home has a new water heater & refrigerator, newer microwave, range & dishwasher.  Also has a washer & dryer.   Home is framed with stainless steel studs throughout.   Not located in a flood zone.    HURRICANE SURVIVOR, WAS NOT FLOODED! MOVE IN READY!
